 933.100984 -166.303237 1225.734021 -125.170151<br>
 320.771418 -163.911119 -148.087080 -332.428961<br></td><td>1.000000<br>
  4427.669962<br></td></tr></table><h3>Explicatie</h3>

<p>la testul <var>1</var> se uneste <var>1 2</var> cu <var>2 2</var> si se obtine lungimea <var>1</var> </p>

